The sun sets alongside a trail of wispy clouds, beyond the Topaz St. Jetty and lifeguard tower.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">トパーズの冬の夕焼け</span>
太陽がかすかな雲の列とともに沈む、トパーズ・ストリートの桟橋とライフガードの塔の向こうに。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The sun sets alongside a trail of wispy clouds, beyond the Topaz St. Jetty and lifeguard tower.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00210-HDR-brighter.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00210-HDR-brighter.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Wires</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241226/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Wires" /><published>2024-12-26T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-26T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/wires</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241226/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Power lines from the AES Redondo Beach power plant.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">電線</span>
AESレッドンドビーチ発電所からの送電線。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Power lines from the AES Redondo Beach power plant.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_DSCF0515_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_DSCF0515_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Holiday Plaza</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241224/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Holiday Plaza" /><published>2024-12-24T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-24T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier-plaza</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241224/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Hermosa’s Pier Plaza, lit up at sunset on Christmas Eve.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ホリデー・プラザ</span>
クリスマスイブの夕暮れ時にライトアップされたハーモサのピア・プラザ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Pier Plaza" /><category term="Lightup" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Hermosa’s Pier Plaza, lit up at sunset on Christmas Eve.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00077_ai-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00077_ai-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Holiday Reflections</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241218/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Holiday Reflections" /><published>2024-12-18T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-18T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241218/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Dusk at the Manhattan Beach Pier, lit up with holiday lights, reflecting on the beach at low tide.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ホリデー・リフレクションズ</span>
マンハッタン・ビーチ・ピアで夕暮れを眺めています。ホリデー・イルミネーションで彩られ、干潮時にはその光がビーチに反射します。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Piers" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Dusk at the Manhattan Beach Pier, lit up with holiday lights, reflecting on the beach at low tide.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09945.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09945.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Afterglow</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241217/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Afterglow" /><published>2024-12-17T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-17T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/mbpier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241217/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   Taken through the supports of the Manhattan Beach Pier, a family on the sand watches the afterglow reflect on the beach. During these extreme low tides, the beach becomes like a mirror.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">残照</span>
マンハッタンビーチピアの支柱を通って撮影された、砂浜で家族が残照がビーチに反射する様子を見守っています。このような極端な干潮時には、ビーチがまるで鏡のようになります。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Piers" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Taken through the supports of the Manhattan Beach Pier, a family on the sand watches the afterglow reflect on the beach. During these extreme low tides, the beach becomes like a mirror.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09940.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09940.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sailboat Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241215/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sailboat Sunset" /><published>2024-12-15T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-15T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sailboat</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241215/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   A sailboat passes by at sunset, at 9th St. in Hermosa Beach.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<!--<span class="title_jp"></span>-->
ハーモサビーチの 9th St.で、夕暮れ時にヨットが通り過ぎます。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A sailboat passes by at sunset, at 9th St. in Hermosa Beach.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09828.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09828.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>